Packages
org.sindice.rdfcommons.beanmapper This package provides classes for Java Bean to RDF mapping.

org.sindice.rdfcommons.jena This package contains Jena specific adapter classes.
org.sindice.rdfcommons.model RDF model interfaces and classes.
org.sindice.rdfcommons.parser Declares RDF parser facilities.
org.sindice.rdfcommons.query Provides classes for RDF query modeling.
org.sindice.rdfcommons.serialization This package provides RDF serialization facilities.
org.sindice.rdfcommons.storage Declares RDF storage specific classes.
org.sindice.rdfcommons.vocabulary Contains all the vocabularies used by this library.
